snippet.title: [TETR.IO] Quick Play #1: Doremy vs. Star (15-02-2020)
snippet.description:
is Star a familiar name for you? you might now her as Ssenbyul, on my Salty Cup S2 videos.

turns out that she is a speed monster if you remove the speed cap from Puyo Puyo Tetris. playing at a consistent 3 pieces/seconds in multiplayer is scary. a difference of 0.5 pieces/seconds can make a huge difference; you gotta be really efficient if you want to put up a fight.

and given how i did not play this kind of tetris game a lot before, my brain can't keep up with both speed and efficiency at the same time...
